sketch.compiler.ast.core

Class NameResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.NameResolver

  • public class NameResolver
extends java.lang.Object
    NameResolver helps translate the name of a struct, function, or variable from the simple name (without package name) to the full name (with package name). The full name will be unique and help distinguish the same simple name in different packages.
